Package: Nothopack
Type: Package
Title: G&Y Forest Simulator for Roble-Rauli-Coigue Stands in Chile
Version: 1.0.0
Author: c(
    person("Salvador", "Gezan", email=forestats.sg@gmail.com", role=c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Paulo", "Moreno", email=paulo.moreno@ciep.cl", role=c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Sebastian", "Palmas", email=palmasforest@gmail.com", role="aut")
Maintainer: Salvador A. Gezan <forestats.sg@gmail.com>
Description: Nothopack is a Growth and Yield simulator for mixed second-growth forests of 
    Roble-Rauli-Coigue from southern Chile. This simulator has inventory processing, 
    stand-level and tree-level simulations with the option of generation of a diameter distribution.
